biotools.summary: Soybean genetic database, is a comprehensive repository for curated genetics, genomics and related data resources for soybean. Contains the most current genetic, physical and genomic sequence maps integrated with qualitative and quantitative traits. SoyBase also contains the well-annotated ''Williams 82'' genomic sequence and associated data mining tools.
